{% call components.section("Best practices") -%}

  <h4>Too many links</h4>

  <p>Do not apply lots of links to paragraph text otherwise a user will have trouble reading the content in its entirety before making a selection.</p>

  {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
    <img src="/assets/link/link-best-practice-1.svg" alt="Link component best practice 1" style="--inline-img-max-width: 561px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>Different link variants</h4>

  <p>Do not use different link variants to direct a user to the same page.</p>

  {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
    <img src="/assets/link/link-best-practice-2.svg" alt="Link component best practice 2" style="--inline-img-max-width: 561px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>Ambiguity</h4>

  <p>When writing link content, avoid ambiguous phrases or a full website URL. A user should have a clear idea of where they are being directed to before they make a selection.</p>

  {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
    <img src="/assets/link/link-best-practice-3.svg" alt="Link component best practice 3" style="--inline-img-max-width: 455px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>Long links</h4>

  <p>Do not apply links to long strings of text.</p>

  {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
    <img src="/assets/link/link-best-practice-4.svg" alt="Link component best practice 4" style="--inline-img-max-width: 561px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>Buttons</h4>

  <p>Buttons have different use cases and should not be used to promote offers or other content.</p>

  <!-- Temporary Default alert until web component release -->
  <p style="background-color: #f2f9f9; border-top: 2px solid #009596; padding: 16px; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.2px;"><span style="color:#003737"><strong>Learn more</strong></span><br />Visit the <a href="https://ux.redhat.com/components/button/" target="_blank">Button</a> component page to learn more about how to use buttons.</p>

